l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use <code>ChatAttachment</code> for compact file previews in messages or prompt composers.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "chat-attachment-default"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"composer\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#composer\" class=\"peer\">Composer</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Pair <code>ChatAttachmentInput</code> with <code>PromptInput</code> to support file picker and drag-and-drop uploads.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "chat-attachment-composer"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<p>When generating local image or video previews with <code>URL.createObjectURL</code>, revoke each <code>blob:</code> URL\nwhen the attachment is removed, when the composer is cleared, and when the component unmounts.</p>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"grouped\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#grouped\" class=\"peer\">Grouped</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use <code>ChatAttachmentGroup</code> to arrange multiple attachments.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "chat-attachment-grouped"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"anatomy\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#anatomy\" class=\"peer\">Anatomy</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<figure dir=\"ltr\" class=\"my-4 bg-fd-card rounded-xl shiki relative border shadow-sm not-prose overflow-hidden text-sm mdx-code-block shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark\" style=\"--shiki-light:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#e1e4e8;--shiki-light-bg:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#24292e\" tabindex=\"-1\"><div class=\"z-1! empty:hidden absolute top-3 right-2 z-2 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-lg text-fd-muted-foreground\"><button aria-label=\"Copy Text\" type=\"button\" class=\"button button--icon-only button--sm button--ghost text-muted -mt-0.5 bg-transparent\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"1em\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 2.5H8A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 6.5 4v1H8a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v1.5h1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 13.5 8V4A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 12 2.5M11 11h1a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H8a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v1H4a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v4a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h4a3 3 0 0 0 3-3zM4 6.5h4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 9.5 8v4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 8 13.5H4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2.5 12V8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4 6.5\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></div><div role=\"region\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"text-[0.8125rem] py-3.5 overflow-auto max-h-[600px]